Dependancy
----------

This program use a modified version of Beep.
Beep written by Jonathan Nightingale and publish under the GNU GPL.
It is a command line tool that beeps the PC speaker. I added a few
line to the code to add an infinite loop option. This version
can be found on my github repository: http://github.com/Nicals/Bepp


Installation
------------

As always:

$ make
# make install

You can remove the program in a similar way:
# make uninstall

